    <topicmeta>
      <linktext>Welcome to DITA-OT Community: Where Code meets Passion</linktext>
      <shortdesc
      >Imagine a scenario where you are facing challenges while working with DITA Open Toolkit. You search for solutions online, check various forums and groups, but find no answers. You feel like you have no one else to turn to. However, there’s one group you haven’t reached out to yet – the DITA-OT community. A “hidden” network of DITA-OT experts, eager to share their knowledge and help you solve your problems. But how do you find them? Who are they? Who belongs to the DITA-OT community? What do we truly know about each other?</shortdesc>
      <author>Justyna Hietala</author>
    </topicmeta>
